~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  Preconditions: req_npc_hostile:bandit,req_money:3000
  (A hostile bandit NPC, player has at least 3000 RU to make the shakedown worthwhile)

  <string id="st_pda_ic_loner_2_precond">
      <text>req_npc_hostile:bandit,req_money:3000</text>
  </string>
